headline.main: Maine's Biggest Dog Sled Race Celebrates 25th Anniversary
headline.print_headline: Maine's Biggest Dog Sled Race Celebrates 25th Anniversary

lead_paragraph: French presidential candidate Francois Fillon, fighting for political survival, called on supporters Saturday not to "abdicate" to those trying to destroy him as the Socialist mayor of Paris asked him to cancel a scheduled rally that would test his staying power.
